QuestData.Title: Slime Time
QuestData.Description:
Murky's a growing boy, he needs to eat! What better than slimeweed for a young murloc?
There's plenty of it around in the water amongst the murlocs; swim through it and feed Murky!
QuestData.LogDescription: Feed Murky $1oa Bunches of Slimeweed by swimming through them.
QuestData.CompletionText: Am I mistaken in thinking you can swim? There's a spell for that.
QuestData.RewardText: Murky seems to have gotten a very strong slime ability due to this slimeweed. Fantastic!
